Cash Management Services

UBA Ghana offers a full range of cash management solutions to meet the varied needs of our corporate customers. With UBA Ghanas cash management solution, a corporate customer can ascertain its exact financial position anytime, anywhere. The customer will also have the flexibility to manage its financial position directly.

Our solution covers payment services, liquidity and information management services as well as cash collection services.

  • Payment Services

  • Liquidity Management

  • Information Management

  • Collections

  • Foreign Exchange
